OL,5,C#4.3m bonus
OL,6, The chairman of JD Sports has rejected
OL,7, criticism of a large bonus he received
OL,8, after the retailer benefited from
OL,9, millions of pounds in Covid support.
OL,11,FPeter Cowgill told the BBC that the
OL,12,F"lion's share" of the #4.3m bonus
OL,13,Frelated to work done pre-January 2019.
OL,15,FHe also rejected suggestions the firm
OL,16,Fshould repay furlough money.
OL,18,FShareholder advisory group Glass Lewis
OL,19,Fhas urged investors in the sportswear
OL,20,Fchain to vote against what it calls an
OL,21,F"inappropriate" pay policy.
